    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape, you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been totally pampered its whole life and looks absolutely flawless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and ready for a new home, this is definitely the one for you. Come take a look\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
