    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor today! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for total perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you! Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
