    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a collector-grade BMW E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example has undergone a comprehensive mechanical refresh, including a reinforced rear subframe and rod bearing replacement for long-term reliability. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is dialed in with Bilstein PSS10 adjustable dampers, ensuring the suspension kinematics remain precise. The exterior retains its factory luster with zero oxidation, and the interior is free of bolster wear, making this a mechanically superior, concours-ready specimen.",
